data.title: Steve Simon & Sam Stosur on Shenzhen hosting the WTA Finals from 2019
data.meta_description: The WTA has selected Shenzhen, China as the host city for the WTA Finals, along with record prize money of $14 million for the Top 8 singles players and doubles teams...
